description: Verify ClothingTrait — wear and remove a lab coat

---

# Go to the server room where the lab coat is
> east
[OK: contains "Server Room"]

# Take the lab coat
> take lab coat
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Wear it
> wear coat
[OK: contains_any "wear" "put on" "Worn" "wearing"]

# Remove it — engine may report "not wearing" due to ClothingTrait integration
